		Search keywords: Event Trigger	

Technical content:
 
		Title: 	Non Blocking Event Trigger	 
 
		Objective: Learning Non Blocking Event Trigger 

		Description: 
		Non blocking events are trigger using ->> operator
                Statement executes without blocking creating non blocking assign update
                Follows NBA semantics
 
		
		Additional setup: None 	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	comp            -- To compile the design
        run             -- To run the design
        all             -- It does all the above steps.
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 
Location Information:
		PATH: 			$VCS_HOME/doc/examples/testbench/sv/NonBlockingEventTrigger
		DIAGRAMS: 		None
	
